ColorPresenter in cli/output/color.go. Independent implementation from Result data; shares prose via package-level constants (markerSyntax). Wraps semantic elements in ANSI sequences per <ref spec="output.color_palette">the palette</ref>. Uses helpers from ansi.go (red, green, yellow, cyan, bold). colorizePatch applies per-line coloring to unified diff output. See <ref spec="output.color_mode">color mode</ref>.